    "body": "Sync `_poll_exclude_pattern` in `_watchfiles.lua` with the new value used for vscode. I.e. remove the `node_modules` pattern.\r\n\r\nSome language servers like tsgo, request watching paths within `node_modules`. The removed pattern is also language/ecosystem specific.\r\n\r\nThe `**` prefixes were preserved, because single `*` or no prefixes didn't work in my tests.",
    "closed_at": "2026-04-28T18:37:13Z",
    "comment_data": [],
    "comment_regular_data": [
        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "need a better explanation than that. node_modules is huge and this will be slow in all other cases besides whatever tsgo situation you mentioned.",
