        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "A `DidChangeWatchedFilesRegistrationOptions` from `tsgo` can include `FileSystemWatcher`s with the following `globPattern`s (formatted):\r\n- globPattern: \"/path/to/project/node_modules/**/*\", reg.id: \"auto-import watcher 16.0\"\r\n- globPattern: \"/path/to/project/node_modules/**/*\", reg.id: \"program files for /path/to/project/subproject-b/tsconfig.json watcher 12.2\"\r\n- globPattern: \"/path/to/project/node_modules/**/*\", reg.id: \"program files for /path/to/project/subproject-c/tsconfig.json watcher 10.2\"\r\n- globPattern: \"/path/to/project/node_modules/@typescript/native-preview-linux-x64/lib/**/*\", reg.id: \"program files for /path/to/project/subproject-a/tsconfig.json watcher 17.1\"\r\n- globPattern: \"/path/to/project/node_modules/@typescript/native-preview-linux-x64/lib/**/*\", reg.id: \"program files for /path/to/project/subproject-b/tsconfig.json watcher 12.1\"\r\n- globPattern: \"/path/to/project/node_modules/@typescript/native-preview-linux-x64/lib/**/*\", reg.id: \"program files for /path/to/project/subproject-c/tsconfig.json watcher 10.1\"\r\n",
